Our plug-in helps you quickly export product-related data and see if you can find the same products at an even lower price。
After installing Dropshipping list exporter plugin,you can open the product list page of your Shopify store and export the product list in Excel format with one click. The plugin also supports analyzing the supply of the products in your store on the AliExpress market. After exporting, you can import the products into other product management platforms for further product selection and management.
